"title": "7773: prophets, role of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7773",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>As agents of God, prophets acted in various capacities, as was required of them, in order to carry out his will and fulfil his purpose.</p>\n<h2>Prophets as God's spokesmen</h2>\n<h3>They heralded impending judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:4\">JON 3:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:7\">1KI 16:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:15-2Kgs22:17\">2KI 22:15–22:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:23-2Chr34:25\">2CH 34:23–34:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:14-Jer1:16\">JER 1:14–1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:14-Jer5:17\">JER 5:14–5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek5:8-Ezek5:12\">EZK 5:8–5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:17\">EZK 38:17</a></p>\n<h3>They advocated repentance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:13\">2KI 17:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:19\">2CH 24:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:12-Jer3:13\">JER 3:12–3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer35:15\">JER 35:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer44:4\">JER 44:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:3-Zech1:6\">ZEC 1:3–1:6</a></p>\n<h3>They conveyed messages from God to the nations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek25:8-Ezek25:11\">EZK 25:8–25:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:13\">JER 46:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer47:1\">JER 47:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:34\">JER 49:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:1\">JER 50:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek25:2\">EZK 25:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek25:12-Ezek25:14\">EZK 25:12–25:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:3\">EZK 26:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:9\">AMO 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek29:2\">EZK 29:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:3\">AMO 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:6\">AMO 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:13\">AMO 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:1\">AMO 2:1</a></p>\n<h2>The supernatural activities of prophets</h2>\n<h3>They revealed future events</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:16-Ezek17:21\">EZK 17:16–17:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:29-1Kgs11:31\">1KI 11:29–11:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:13\">1KI 20:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:13-Isa7:14\">ISA 7:13–7:14</a> <em>the birth of Immanuel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:10\">JER 29:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:38-Dan2:44\">DAN 2:38–2:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:2\">DAN 9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:15\">MAT 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1\">HOS 11:1</a>MAT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:17-Hos2:18\">2:17–2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:15\">JER 31:15</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:17\">MAT 8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:4\">ISA 53:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:18\">ACT 3:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:27-Acts11:29\">ACT 11:27–11:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:10-Acts21:11\">ACT 21:10–21:11</a></p>\n<h3>They received dreams and visions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:6\">NUM 12:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:26\">EZK 7:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:1\">DAN 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:1\">DAN 8:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:10\">HOS 12:10</a></p>\n<h3>They worked miracles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:3\">2KI 5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:13-1Kgs17:24\">1KI 17:13–17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:3-2Kgs4:6\">2KI 4:3–4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:15-2Kgs4:17\">2KI 4:15–4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:32-2Kgs4:35\">2KI 4:32–4:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:40-2Kgs4:44\">2KI 4:40–4:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:5-2Kgs6:6\">2KI 6:5–6:6</a></p>\n<h2>Prophets as intermediaries</h2>\n<h3>Between God and the people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:16-Deut18:18\">DEU 18:16–18:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:30-Exod7:1\">EXO 6:30–7:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:4-2Sam7:7\">2SA 7:4–7:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:7-2Sam12:14\">2SA 12:7–12:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:24-2Sam12:25\">2SA 12:24–12:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:11-2Sam24:12\">2SA 24:11–24:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:42\">1KI 20:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:1\">2KI 20:1</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:1\">ISA 38:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:5\">2CH 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr28:9-2Chr28:11\">2CH 28:9–28:11</a></p>\n<h3>Between the people and God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:9\">1SA 7:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:7\">GEN 20:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:11\">2KI 20:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:20\">2CH 32:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:14\">JER 11:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:18\">JER 27:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek14:7\">EZK 14:7</a></p>\n<h3>Their responsibility as watchmen</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:17-Ezek3:21\">EZK 3:17–3:21</a></strong> <em>The intermediary role of the prophet is highlighted by the image of a watchman who receives messages from God and conveys them to the people.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:1-Ezek33:7\">EZK 33:1–33:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:8\">HOS 9:8</a></p>\n<h2>Prophets as leaders in the community</h2>\n<h3>They gave advice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:2-Zech7:3\">ZEC 7:2–7:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:6\">1SA 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:6\">1KI 22:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:11\">2KI 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:8-2Kgs6:10\">2KI 6:8–6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:14\">2KI 22:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:22\">2CH 34:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:25\">2CH 29:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:2\">ISA 37:2</a></p>\n<h3>They gave encouragement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:32\">ACT 15:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:1-Ezra5:2\">EZR 5:1–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:4-Jer29:7\">JER 29:4–29:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:17-Ezek11:21\">EZK 11:17–11:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:13\">HAG 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:4\">HAG 2:4</a></p>\n<h3>They led the people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:13\">HOS 12:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:15\">DEU 18:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:6\">1SA 7:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:40\">1KI 18:40</a></p>\n<h3>They appointed kings and leaders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:1\">1SA 10:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:13\">1SA 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:34\">1KI 1:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:38\">1KI 1:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:15-1Kgs19:16\">1KI 19:15–19:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:6\">2KI 9:6</a></p>\n<h2>Prophets as writers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:29\">1CH 29:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:29\">2CH 9:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr13:22\">2CH 13:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:22\">2CH 26:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:32\">2CH 32:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:8\">ISA 30:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:2\">JER 30:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:4\">JER 36:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:60\">JER 51:60</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:11\">EZK 43:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:2\">HAB 2:2</a></p>",
